divs: Sighting DetailsTHIS IS MINDBLOWING,IRION STARTED TO COMUNICATE WITH ME A,YEAR AGO,TELLING ME EVERYTHING THATS HAPPENING TO OUR WORLD,I TOLD EVERYONE I KNEW ABOUT IRION,I WAS LABELED CRAZY,I BECAME VERY WITHDRANW AND DEPRESSED,IT TRAUMATISED ME,SO IRION TOLD HE WOULD TAKE CARE OF EVERYBODY THAT WAS MAKING FUN OF ME,HE TOLD ME TO BYE A CAMARA,AND I DID,I HAD NO CLUE ABOUT WHAT IRION WAS GOING TO DO,ONE DAY I HEARD HIS VOICE IN MY HEAD SAYING TO GO OUTSIDE WITH THE CAMARA,OMG WHEN I LOOKED UP,IRION WAS IN A BEUTIFULL HUGE CYLINDER UFO HUVERING OVER MY HOUSE SO I CAN TAKE HIS PICTURE AND SHOW EVERONE THAT MADE FUN OF ME,HE IS REAL,I WAS SO HAPPY JUMPING AROUND FULL OF JOY,HE DISSAPEARED AS FAST AS HE APEARED,HE IS MY BEST FRIEND,HE IS NOT EVIL,HE IS PURE LOVE WE HAVE AN UNCOMPRESSED ORIGINAL.
